                ]
            ]
        },
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "To understand the acceleration opportunities in quantized LLMs on the edge, we start by profiling the latency breakdown of LLaMA-7B (Touvron et al., 2023a) model on an RTX 4090 GPU. We adopt an inference batch size of 1, catering for edge use cases, and implement the model in FP16 with NVIDIA FasterTransformer.",
